Package: smlmkalman
Type: Package
Title: Functions for generating filamentous SMLM datasets and a crescent-based Kalman Filter for image segmentation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Andrew", "Buist", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "ab1051@exeter.ac.uk"))
Author: Andrew Buist [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Andrew Buist <ab1051@exeter.ac.uk>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0), stats, spdep, pracma, scales, truncnorm
Description: generate_filaments() creates a dataset made to simulate those produced in DNA-PAINT imaging of plant microtubules.
    crescent_kf() uses a local datapoint distributions to perform Kalman Filtering on data without time information.
License: use_mit_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
